      • determineInflections

        public static void determineInflections(Inflections.InflectionType inflectionType,
                                        java.util.HashSet<java.lang.String> baseFormSet)
        This method generates the requested type of inflection for a set of verbs or nouns. This generation is done using the Morphg morphological generator tool, developed by John A. Carroll.
        Parameters:
        inflectionType - the type of inflections
        baseFormSet - the set of verbs or nouns
